Crimson Wine Group - Investor Overview

































Crimson Wine Group




Investor Overview





 


 


‹
›


Crimson Wine Group is a Napa, CA, based owner and operator of boutique, estate-based wineries that produce world class wines in the finest wine growing regions of California, Oregon and Washington.  Crimson’s wineries include Pine Ridge Vineyards, Seghesio Family Vineyards, Archery Summit Winery, Chamisal Vineyards, Double Canyon Vineyards and Seven Hills Winery.  Since its founding in 1991, Crimson has been committed to the highest quality appellations and vineyard sites of each region, with the highest respect for the land. Each CWG property produces distinct varietal wines that reflect the finest characteristics of their place of origin. 



